'''朝鮮民主主義人民共和國官邸'''指的是為[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]領導人辦公或生活而修的豪華[[招待所|招待所]]建築群。根據[[金正日|金正日]]前保鑣[[李英國|李英國]]的描述，朝鮮境內現有十餘座領導人[[官邸|官邸]]<ref>{{cite news |title=The Supremo in His Labyrinth |work=Time Magazine |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,201976-1,00.html |accessdate=December 12, 2012 |first=Donald |last=Macintyre |date=February 18, 2002 |archive-date=2013-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731023955/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,201976-1,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而根據[[北韓揭秘計劃|北韓揭秘計劃]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Prynne|first=Miranda|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-uncovered-palaces-labour-camps-and-mass-graves-1711573.html|title=North Korea uncovered: Palaces, labour camps and mass graves|work=The Independent|date=June 21, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307232604/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-uncovered-palaces-labour-camps-and-mass-graves-1711573.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，很多都可以通過衛星圖像識別出來<ref>{{cite web |title = The Palaces of Pyongyang on Google Earth |work = One Free Korea |url = http://freekorea.us/2009/08/12/the-palaces-of-pyongyang/ |accessdate = December 12, 2012 |archive-date = 2020-06-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200623043702/https://freekorea.us/2009/08/12/the-palaces-of-pyongyang/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。其中，[[龍城官邸|龍城官邸]]是現任最高領導人[[金正恩|金正恩]]的核心官邸<ref>{{cite web |title = Kim Jong-il's ‘Mt. Ryongnam Range’ is succeeded by Kim Jong-un's ‘Mt. Ami Range’ |work = Leonid Petrov's Korea Vision |url = http://leonidpetrov.wordpress.com/2011/02/16/kim-jong-ils-mt-ryongnam-range-is-succeeded-by-kim-jong-uns-mt-ami-range/ |accessdate = December 12, 2012 |archive-date = 2020-11-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201113184334/https://leonidpetrov.wordpress.com/2011/02/16/kim-jong-ils-mt-ryongnam-range-is-succeeded-by-kim-jong-uns-mt-ami-range/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。所有官邸都是朝鮮當局的保密對象，只有極少數舊照從中流出<ref>{{cite news|last=Han|first=Young Jin|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|title=Kim Jong Il, Where He Sleeps and Where He Works|work=DailyNK|date=March 15, 2005|accessdate=December 12, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516044422/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|archivedate=2013年5月16日|df=}}</ref>。

